 <arm>
   <uof name="basic_geometric_topology">
     <description>
The basic_geometric_topology UoF specifies the data structure for the description of topological vertices, edges and faces 
with associated geometry. An edge curve is bounded topologically by two vertices and its geometry is defined by reference to a geometric curve.
 A face surface is bounded topologically by one oor more loops of edges and its internal geometry is defined by reference to a geometric surface.
 </description>
     
